    <Note Title="Topic" Type="Summary" Ordinal="1" xml:lang="en">Security update for quassel</Note>
    <Note Title="Details" Type="General" Ordinal="2" xml:lang="en">The distributed IRC client quassel was updated to fix one security issue.

The following vulnerability was fixed:

* CVE-2015-3427: The SQL injection fix for CVE-2013-4422 was incomplete (boo#928728)
